### Créer un utilisateur
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "firstname": "Alice",
  "lastname": "Dupont",
  "email": "alice@test.com",
  "password": "pass1234"
}

### Créer compte 1
POST http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Compte Courant",
  "type": "checking"
}

### Créer compte 2
POST http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Livret A",
  "type": "savings"
}

### Créer compte 3
POST http://localhost:3000/users/1/accounts
